<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Āṇṭār tiruveṇṇainalluruṭaiyāṉ
<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yataraṉ terinta kaikoḷarukkuk kottu
<lb n="3"/>varkaḷum kūṟuceyvārkaḷum niyamattomum ku
<lb n="4"/>paṭavarum mayil veṭṭaikkāṟarum Ivvaṉaivom
<lb n="5"/>ṅkaḷ maṭappuṟamākak kuṭutta nilamāvatu kīḻpāṟkellai
</p>

</div>

<div type="apparatus">

</div>

<div type="translation" source="bib:Gillet2024_01">

<p>Line 1: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> the lord <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>uṭaiyāṉ</foreign></supplied> of Tiruveṇṇainallūr <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </p><p>Line 2: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> to the Kaikkōḷar <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kaikoḷarukku</foreign></supplied> who knew (<foreign>terinta</foreign>? Probably for <foreign>teṟinta</foreign>, to destroy) Jayataraṉ (a name of a person or of a place?) <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </p><p>Line 3: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> the officers who apportion <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kūṟuceyvārkaḷum</foreign></supplied> and we of the religious duty <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>niyamattōmum</foreign></supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </p><p>Line 5: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> this is the land <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>nilamāvatu</foreign></supplied> that was given <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kuṭutta</foreign></supplied> as <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>āka</foreign></supplied> cultivable land <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>puṟam</foreign></supplied> to the <foreign>maṭam</foreign> <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>maṭa</foreign></supplied> of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> : the eastern side boundary <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kīḻpāṟkellai</foreign></supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </p></div>

